# Workspace Health Docs

Use `enclosure workspace health` to check the project-local contract before drilling into workspace commands.

## Common Workflows

- Run after editing `.enclosure/enclosure.yaml`, rules, or recipes.
- Use `enclosure workspace rules` when rule documents have findings.
- Use `enclosure workspace recipe --check` when recipe templates have findings.

## Reading Results

- Config, rules, and recipe failures are blocking findings.
- Missing recipes are informational unless recipe manifests exist and fail validation or rendering.
- Root `enclosure health` includes this report before architecture health.

## Related Commands

- `enclosure health --docs`
- `enclosure workspace rules --docs`
- `enclosure workspace recipe --docs`
